Package: abmi.camera.extras
Type: Package
Title: Extra functions and data to make use of ABMI camera deployment data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
  person("Marcus", "Becker", email = "mabecker@ualberta.ca", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Maintainer: Marcus Becker <mabecker@ualberta.ca>
Description: This packages provides some functionality to interact with and explore ABMI camera data. 
  It includes some sample data, important lookup tables, and a few functions to serve basic needs.
